{"tid":735842,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【民進黨第一腳膠】國發會副主委地鐵偷拍台妹腳斷正","createTime":"2018-07-09T20:55:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-10T00:57:30.000Z","uid":109462,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2b52d3a6c1f8d6a2d832d10f570795fd79ae52f9","tid":735842,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T20:55:58.000Z","msg":"【打臉偷拍官員】「不慎失手」　邱俊榮卻刪除高達35張照片<br />\n建立時間：2018/07/08 17:46<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180708/640_57909df04253f06c55644d8f83858c32.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180708%2F640_57909df04253f06c55644d8f83858c32.jpg&h=398e2999&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n國發會副主委邱俊榮疑似在捷運站偷拍女子背影、大腿被民眾抓包，並現場被要求刪除所拍照片。雖然邱俊榮發出聲明，強調是不慎失手，不過依據網友提供的影片，邱刪除的照片卻高達35張，令人匪夷所思。<br />\n<br />\n根據洪姓網友在爆料公社上傳的影片，邱俊榮在刪除照片時，不斷說不好意思，依據影片內容，光是勾選照片，進行刪除，就高達35張照片。（財經中心／台北報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.finance.appledaily.com/realtime/20180708/1387522/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.finance.appledaily.com%2Frealtime%2F20180708%2F1387522%2F&d=C10G%2FRT8B9Z%2B5xCVxkotQY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=ed5ffbec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.finance.appledaily.com%2Frealtime%2F20180708%2F1387522%2F&h=30e96679\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.finance.appledaily.com/realtime/20180708/1387522/</a>"},{"pid":"7c9fb7986b3d8bfadcbcdd3b2999b22b4ca49b7c","tid":735842,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T20:58:01.000Z","msg":"疑涉及西門町偷拍案　國發會副主委邱俊榮請辭獲准<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/storage.googleapis.com/nownews2017/nownews_production/images/5b41d52349e7bf4adb967249_201807081710.jpg?w=640&amp;q=70&amp;src=https://rssimg.nownews.com/images/5b41d52349e7bf4adb967249_201807081710.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Fnownews2017%2Fnownews_production%2Fimages%2F5b41d52349e7bf4adb967249_201807081710.jpg%3Fw%3D640%26q%3D70%26src%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Frssimg.nownews.com%2Fimages%2F5b41d52349e7bf4adb967249_201807081710.jpg&h=3072f289&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n國發會副主委邱俊榮日前傳出在西門町涉及疑似偷拍女性案件，警方今日已受理報案，邱俊榮今（8）日下午發出聲明道歉，已口頭請辭；國發會主委陳美伶今（8）日晚間也發出聲明指出，邱副主委願意坦然面對調查，已經同意他請辭國發會副主委一職，並向行政院長賴清德報告。<br />\n<br />\n台北市政府警察局萬華分局漢中街派出所表示，大約在下午1點接獲民眾報案，指昨天下午約4點在捷運西門站遭偷拍，目前正由北市府警察局捷運警察隊調閱相關監視器畫面，將請涉案人 (國發會副主委邱俊榮) 到案說明，以釐清案發當下情形。<br />\n<br />\n對於此事引發的風波，邱俊榮表示，要向當事人及社會鄭重致歉，但基於此事件已影響內閣形象及政府運作，傍晚已向陳主委口頭請辭並獲准。<br />\n<br />\n陳美伶也在晚間發布聲明指出：「邱副主委俊榮在今天傍晚向我表示該事件已造成內閣形象的傷害，他願意坦然面對調查，並再次向該女士表示歉意。」<br />\n<br />\n陳美伶表示，邱副主委已請辭國發會副主委一職，「本人已同意並向賴院長報告。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.nownews.com/news/2785379?from=mar\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.nownews.com%2Fnews%2F2785379%3Ffrom%3Dmar&d=C10G%2FRT8B9Z%2B5xCVxkotQY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=9b52ec3e\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.nownews.com/news/2785379?from=mar</a>"},{"pid":"611bd4f739e059be829f12835bce7e6a7553d63d","tid":735842,"uid":94828,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T23:41:31.000Z","msg":"個樣好痴漢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d55b7c11211de638683362a8f25bef0f1e4e5f12","tid":735842,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T23:46:19.000Z","msg":"咁撚樣都做到國發會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"898ce667b02ddb89cc58de9b333e2d691c318e7a","tid":735842,"uid":116530,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d55b7c11211de638683362a8f25bef0f1e4e5f12","tid":735842,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T23:46:19.000Z","msg":"咁撚樣都做到國發會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T23:56:58.000Z","msg":"台灣人就係咁垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aca79278495b789f161115d617882549b33d694c","tid":735842,"uid":121249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T00:16:56.000Z","msg":"台妹咁正 點忍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03256199a943ed667d854ffa91f6d867491ce592","tid":735842,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T00:21:00.000Z","msg":"拍下好小事"},{"pid":"edea6ed3bf03ba61f54cc828a68fc6b5890c2f16","tid":735842,"uid":52595,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T00:22:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1b199bf44e6cf00511f0873ba28eb6c1643df1fb","tid":735842,"uid":166288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T00:44:13.000Z","msg":"個樣有潛質去拍戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c45b96924a11f83279ed334517414c19bca5cf8f","tid":735842,"uid":127611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T00:45:44.000Z","msg":"台妹啲腿真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔似港女啲水腫腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc572e0a7c069d3719fda55a05fbfc86742e3b45","tid":735842,"uid":119778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T00:45:47.000Z","msg":"台灣不意外"},{"pid":"8ab182c6736a130779f5c33bb3a3fa8a38703c86","tid":735842,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T00:50:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"97bbae6a483fe43da7f92a8631a5885ec3515003","tid":735842,"uid":91664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T00:57:30.000Z","msg":"冇圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}